		  <p>We don't want to become another large research firm that charges outrageous rates for its work. In most cases, your research will be limited to a few pages, so it's hard to justify charging such a premium. In any case, we're hoping that your motivation is more than just money. It's hard to build a follower base if you're charging too much: our model is low price, high volume.</p>
